    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Career Strategy\"\nformat:\n  html:\n    toc: true\n    code-fold: true\nexecute:\n  echo: true\n  eval: true\n  warning: false\n---\n\n\n## Overview\n\nThis page synthesizes our findings from EDA and skill gap analysis into actionable career strategies for each team member.\n\n::: {#setup-career .cell execution_count=1}\n``` {.python .cell-code code-summary=\"Load libraries\"}\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nimport plotly.express as px\nimport plotly.graph_objects as go\nimport plotly.io as pio\nimport warnings\nwarnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n\n# ── Apply consistent Plotly theme ────────────────────────────────────────\ncustom_template = go.layout.Template()\ncustom_template.layout = go.Layout(\n    font=dict(family=\"Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif\", size=13, color=\"#2c3e50\"),\n    title=dict(font=dict(size=20, color=\"#2c3e50\"), x=0.5, xanchor=\"center\"),\n    paper_bgcolor=\"white\",\n    plot_bgcolor=\"#f8f9fa\",\n    colorway=[\"#3498db\", \"#e74c3c\", \"#2ecc71\", \"#f39c12\", \"#9b59b6\",\n              \"#1abc9c\", \"#e67e22\", \"#34495e\", \"#16a085\", \"#c0392b\"],\n    xaxis=dict(gridcolor=\"#dee2e6\", linecolor=\"#adb5bd\"),\n    yaxis=dict(gridcolor=\"#dee2e6\", linecolor=\"#adb5bd\"),\n    hoverlabel=dict(font_size=12),\n    margin=dict(t=60, b=40, l=50, r=30),\n)\npio.templates[\"job_market\"] = custom_template\npio.templates.default = \"job_market\"\n```\n:::\n\n\n## 1. Market-Aligned Career Paths\n\nBased on our analysis, these career paths align with current market demand:\n\n::: {#cell-career-paths .cell execution_count=2}\n``` {.python .cell-code code-summary=\"Career path alignment\"}\npaths = pd.DataFrame({\n    \"Career Path\": [\n        \"Data Analyst\",\n        \"Data Scientist\",\n        \"Data Engineer\",\n        \"ML Engineer\",\n        \"Cloud/DevOps Engineer\"\n    ],\n    \"Core Skills Required\": [\n        \"Python, SQL, Tableau, Excel, Communication\",\n        \"Python, SQL, Machine Learning, Deep Learning, R\",\n        \"Python, SQL, Spark, AWS, Docker, ETL\",\n        \"Python, Machine Learning, Deep Learning, Docker, Cloud\",\n        \"AWS, Docker, Kubernetes, Linux, Git\"\n    ],\n    \"Avg Salary Range\": [\n        \"$55K – $85K\",\n        \"$85K – $130K\",\n        \"$90K – $140K\",\n        \"$100K – $150K\",\n        \"$95K – $145K\"\n    ],\n    \"Job Availability\": [\n        \"Very High\",\n        \"High\",\n        \"High\",\n        \"High\",\n        \"Very High\"\n    ]\n})\n\npaths.style.set_properties(**{\n    'text-align': 'left',\n    'white-space': 'pre-wrap'\n})\n```\n\n::: {#career-paths .cell-output .cell-output-display execution_count=2}\n```{=html}\n<style type=\"text/css\">\n#T_32405_row0_col0, #T_32405_row0_col1, #T_32405_row0_col2, #T_32405_row0_col3, #T_32405_row1_col0, #T_32405_row1_col1, #T_32405_row1_col2, #T_32405_row1_col3, #T_32405_row2_col0, #T_32405_row2_col1, #T_32405_row2_col2, #T_32405_row2_col3, #T_32405_row3_col0, #T_32405_row3_col1, #T_32405_row3_col2, #T_32405_row3_col3, #T_32405_row4_col0, #T_32405_row4_col1, #T_32405_row4_col2, #T_32405_row4_col3 {\n  text-align: left;\n  white-space: pre-wrap;\n}\n</style>\n<table id=\"T_32405\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th class=\"blank level0\" >&nbsp;</th>\n      <th id=\"T_32405_level0_col0\" class=\"col_heading level0 col0\" >Career Path</th>\n      <th id=\"T_32405_level0_col1\" class=\"col_heading level0 col1\" >Core Skills Required</th>\n      <th id=\"T_32405_level0_col2\" class=\"col_heading level0 col2\" >Avg Salary Range</th>\n      <th id=\"T_32405_level0_col3\" class=\"col_heading level0 col3\" >Job Availability</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th id=\"T_32405_level0_row0\" class=\"row_heading level0 row0\" >0</th>\n      <td id=\"T_32405_row0_col0\" class=\"data row0 col0\" >Data Analyst</td>\n      <td id=\"T_32405_row0_col1\" class=\"data row0 col1\" >Python, SQL, Tableau, Excel, Communication</td>\n      <td id=\"T_32405_row0_col2\" class=\"data row0 col2\" >$55K – $85K</td>\n      <td id=\"T_32405_row0_col3\" class=\"data row0 col3\" >Very High</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th id=\"T_32405_level0_row1\" class=\"row_heading level0 row1\" >1</th>\n      <td id=\"T_32405_row1_col0\" class=\"data row1 col0\" >Data Scientist</td>\n      <td id=\"T_32405_row1_col1\" class=\"data row1 col1\" >Python, SQL, Machine Learning, Deep Learning, R</td>\n      <td id=\"T_32405_row1_col2\" class=\"data row1 col2\" >$85K – $130K</td>\n      <td id=\"T_32405_row1_col3\" class=\"data row1 col3\" >High</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th id=\"T_32405_level0_row2\" class=\"row_heading level0 row2\" >2</th>\n      <td id=\"T_32405_row2_col0\" class=\"data row2 col0\" >Data Engineer</td>\n      <td id=\"T_32405_row2_col1\" class=\"data row2 col1\" >Python, SQL, Spark, AWS, Docker, ETL</td>\n      <td id=\"T_32405_row2_col2\" class=\"data row2 col2\" >$90K – $140K</td>\n      <td id=\"T_32405_row2_col3\" class=\"data row2 col3\" >High</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th id=\"T_32405_level0_row3\" class=\"row_heading level0 row3\" >3</th>\n      <td id=\"T_32405_row3_col0\" class=\"data row3 col0\" >ML Engineer</td>\n      <td id=\"T_32405_row3_col1\" class=\"data row3 col1\" >Python, Machine Learning, Deep Learning, Docker, Cloud</td>\n      <td id=\"T_32405_row3_col2\" class=\"data row3 col2\" >$100K – $150K</td>\n      <td id=\"T_32405_row3_col3\" class=\"data row3 col3\" >High</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th id=\"T_32405_level0_row4\" class=\"row_heading level0 row4\" >4</th>\n      <td id=\"T_32405_row4_col0\" class=\"data row4 col0\" >Cloud/DevOps Engineer</td>\n      <td id=\"T_32405_row4_col1\" class=\"data row4 col1\" >AWS, Docker, Kubernetes, Linux, Git</td>\n      <td id=\"T_32405_row4_col2\" class=\"data row4 col2\" >$95K – $145K</td>\n      <td id=\"T_32405_row4_col3\" class=\"data row4 col3\" >Very High</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n```\n:::\n:::\n\n\n## 2. 90-Day Action Plan\n\n::: {#action-plan-visual .cell execution_count=3}\n``` {.python .cell-code code-summary=\"90-day learning timeline\"}\ntimeline = pd.DataFrame({\n    \"Phase\": [\"Month 1\"] * 3 + [\"Month 2\"] * 3 + [\"Month 3\"] * 3,\n    \"Task\": [\n        \"Complete Python/SQL refresher\",\n        \"Set up cloud account (AWS Free Tier)\",\n        \"Begin ML fundamentals course\",\n        \"Build a portfolio project\",\n        \"Earn one cloud certification\",\n        \"Practice with real datasets (Kaggle)\",\n        \"Deploy a project to cloud\",\n        \"Start networking & applying\",\n        \"Conduct mock interviews\"\n    ],\n    \"Category\": [\n        \"Technical\", \"Cloud\", \"ML\",\n        \"Portfolio\", \"Cloud\", \"Technical\",\n        \"Cloud\", \"Career\", \"Career\"\n    ]\n})\n\nfig = px.timeline(\n    pd.DataFrame({\n        \"Task\": timeline[\"Task\"],\n        \"Start\": pd.to_datetime([\n            \"2024-01-01\", \"2024-01-08\", \"2024-01-15\",\n            \"2024-02-01\", \"2024-02-08\", \"2024-02-15\",\n            \"2024-03-01\", \"2024-03-08\", \"2024-03-15\"\n        ]),\n        \"End\": pd.to_datetime([\n            \"2024-01-28\", \"2024-01-28\", \"2024-01-28\",\n            \"2024-02-28\", \"2024-02-28\", \"2024-02-28\",\n            \"2024-03-28\", \"2024-03-28\", \"2024-03-28\"\n        ]),\n        \"Phase\": timeline[\"Phase\"]\n    }),\n    x_start=\"Start\", x_end=\"End\", y=\"Task\",\n    color=\"Phase\",\n    title=\"90-Day Career Development Timeline\"\n)\nfig.update_layout(height=450, yaxis=dict(autorange=\"reversed\"))\nfig.show()\n```\n\n::: {#action-plan-visual-1 .cell-output .cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n        <script>\n        window.PlotlyConfig = {MathJaxConfig: 'local'};\n        if (window.MathJax && window.MathJax.Hub && window.MathJax.Hub.Config) {window.MathJax.Hub.Config({SVG: {font: \"STIX-Web\"}});}\n        </script>\n        <script type=\"module\">import \"https://cdn.plot.ly/plotly-3.5.0.min\"</script>\n        \n```\n:::\n\n::: {#action-plan-visual-2 .cell-output .cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<div>            <script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/mathjax/2.7.5/MathJax.js?config=TeX-AMS-MML_SVG\"></script><script>if (window.MathJax && window.MathJax.Hub && window.MathJax.Hub.Config) {window.MathJax.Hub.Config({SVG: {font: \"STIX-Web\"}});}</script>                <script>window.PlotlyConfig = {MathJaxConfig: 'local'};</script>\n        <script charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"https://cdn.plot.ly/plotly-3.5.0.min.js\" integrity=\"sha256-fHbNLP+GlIXN+efbQec78UkemUz3NJp7UmfGxC1tNxs=\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>                <div id=\"18e25fed-137b-4361-b934-09d4ec5b229a\" class=\"plotly-graph-div\" style=\"height:450px; width:100%;\"></div>            <script>                window.PLOTLYENV=window.PLOTLYENV || {};                                if (document.getElementById(\"18e25fed-137b-4361-b934-09d4ec5b229a\")) {                    Plotly.newPlot(                        \"18e25fed-137b-4361-b934-09d4ec5b229a\",                        [{\"base\":[\"2024-01-01T00:00:00.000000\",\"2024-01-08T00:00:00.000000\",\"2024-01-15T00:00:00.000000\"],\"hovertemplate\":\"Phase=Month 1\\u003cbr\\u003eStart=%{base}\\u003cbr\\u003eEnd=%{x}\\u003cbr\\u003eTask=%{y}\\u003cextra\\u003e\\u003c\\u002fextra\\u003e\",\"legendgroup\":\"Month 1\",\"marker\":{\"color\":\"#3498db\",\"pattern\":{\"shape\":\"\"}},\"name\":\"Month 1\",\"orientation\":\"h\",\"showlegend\":true,\"textposition\":\"auto\",\"x\":[2332800000,1728000000,1123200000],\"xaxis\":\"x\",\"y\":[\"Complete Python\\u002fSQL refresher\",\"Set up cloud account (AWS Free Tier)\",\"Begin ML fundamentals course\"],\"yaxis\":\"y\",\"type\":\"bar\"},{\"base\":[\"2024-02-01T00:00:00.000000\",\"2024-02-08T00:00:00.000000\",\"2024-02-15T00:00:00.000000\"],\"hovertemplate\":\"Phase=Month 2\\u003cbr\\u003eStart=%{base}\\u003cbr\\u003eEnd=%{x}\\u003cbr\\u003eTask=%{y}\\u003cextra\\u003e\\u003c\