ecution_count=4}\n```{=html}\n<div>\n<style scoped>\n    .dataframe tbody tr th:only-of-type {\n        vertical-align: middle;\n    }\n\n    .dataframe tbody tr th {\n        vertical-align: top;\n    }\n\n    .dataframe thead th {\n        text-align: right;\n    }\n</style>\n<table border=\"1\" class=\"dataframe\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr style=\"text-align: right;\">\n      <th></th>\n      <th>Certification</th>\n      <th>Relevance</th>\n      <th>Difficulty</th>\n      <th>Approx. Cost</th>\n      <th>Time to Complete</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th>0</th>\n      <td>AWS Cloud Practitioner</td>\n      <td>Cloud</td>\n      <td>Beginner</td>\n      <td>$100</td>\n      <td>2-4 weeks</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th>1</th>\n      <td>AWS Solutions Architect – Associate</td>\n      <td>Cloud</td>\n      <td>Intermediate</td>\n      <td>$150</td>\n      <td>4-8 weeks</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th>2</th>\n      <td>Google Data Analytics (Coursera)</td>\n      <td>Analytics</td>\n      <td>Beginner</td>\n      <td>$49/mo</td>\n      <td>6 months</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th>3</th>\n      <td>Tableau Desktop Specialist</td>\n      <td>Visualization</td>\n      <td>Intermediate</td>\n      <td>$100</td>\n      <td>2-4 weeks</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th>4</th>\n      <td>Microsoft Azure Fundamentals (AZ-900)</td>\n      <td>Cloud</td>\n      <td>Beginner</td>\n      <td>Free</td>\n      <td>1-2 weeks</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th>5</th>\n      <td>IBM Data Science Professional Certificate</td>\n      <td>Data Science</td>\n      <td>Intermediate</td>\n      <td>$49/mo</td>\n      <td>4-6 months</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n```\n:::\n:::\n\n\n## Summary\n\nThe IT job market in 2024 heavily favors candidates with a blend of programming fundamentals (Python, SQL), cloud literacy (AWS, Docker), and domain-specific expertise (ML, data visualization). By following the structured improvement plan fro